'''桑德拉·李·克里斯蒂安森'''（{{Lang-en|Sandra Lee Christiansen}}，{{bd|1966年|7月3日|||catIdx=Christiansen}}）是[[美国|美国]]{{Link-en|厨师名流|Celebrity chef|电视厨师}}兼[[作家|作家]]<ref name="Payne">{{cite web |author1=Patti Payne |title=Food Network star Sandra Lee peeled onions as a youth at the Puyallup Fair |url=https://www.bizjournals.com/seattle/stories/2007/05/14/tidbits1.html |publisher=The Business Journals |accessdate=2021-03-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727093654/https://www.bizjournals.com/seattle/stories/2007/05/14/tidbits1.html |archivedate=2018-07-27 |date=2007-05-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Biography">{{cite web |title=Sandra Lee Biography |url=https://www.biography.com/people/sandra-lee--20906429 |publisher=The Biography.com |accessdate=2021-03-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723212431/https://www.biography.com/people/sandra-lee--20906429 |archivedate=2018-07-23 |date=2015-05-13}}</ref>。她以“半自制式（Semi-Homemade）”烹饪概念而闻名；她对此解释为烹饪时使用七成的预包装产品和三成的新鲜食材<ref>{{cite web |author1=Gully Wells |title=Sandra Lee: The Woman in White |url=https://www.vogue.com/article/sandra-lee-the-woman-in-white |publisher=[[时尚_(Vogue)|Vogue]] |accessdate=2021-03-12 |archive-date=2016-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026103558/http://www.vogue.com/865456/sandra-lee-the-woman-in-white |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她因为她的主持及表演而获得了2012年度{{Link-en|日间艾美奖最佳生活及烹饪节目主持人|Daytime Emmy Award for Outstanding Lifestyle/Culinary Show Host}}。而作为现任[[纽约州|纽约州]][[州长|州长]][[安德鲁·库默|安德鲁·库默]]的伴侣，她在2011年到2019年的时间里担任着纽约州[[de_facto|事实上]]的[[第一夫人|州长夫人]]。

